otherNames: Sayonara, Tyrano, さよなら, ティラノ, 안녕, 티라노: 영원히, 함께, My TYRANO: Together, Forever
synopsis: Two dinosaurs, differently unfit for life, a T-Rex who doesn't want to be a predator and a little pterodactyl who doesn't want to fly, begin a long and hard journey to reach a legendary valley called Paradise
